data.description: LOCATION! LOCATION! LOCATION! Great opportunity to own this fully detached single family located in the heart of New Dorp. This house offers 3 bedrooms, 2 baths and basement. Conveniently located half block to Hylan Blvd, both local and express buses, LA Fitness, Starbucks, HL Supermarket, Shoprite, Stop and Shop, restaurants, Too Much to Mention!! 1st floor features front porch, foyer, kitchen, living room, dining room, half bath, access to the backyard. 2nd floor features 3 bedrooms, 1 full bath, and attic. Basement: partial finished, separate side entrance, utilities, storage, laundry. Driveway runs all the way back to the detached garage at the back of the yard. Call today for your private showing!!
